To separate **Programs** and **Projects**, we will treat them as two distinct, top-level tracks. This makes a clear structural distinction for your users: **Programs** represent your ongoing, long-term community setups (like *Healing Circles*), while **Projects** highlight targeted, time-bound initiatives (like environmental campaigns or local structural builds).
We have updated the layout and implementation code below to seamlessly integrate the official **Camel Logo** alongside the **NVCBO branding** in the header section of the sidebar, matching your brand asset configuration.
